- [x] [BEHAVIOR] migration 164 在 DO $$ 块中同时添加 started_at 和 completed_at 列
  Test: manual: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const c=fs.readFileSync('packages/brain/migrations/164_fix_missing_columns.sql','utf8');if(!c.includes('started_at'))process.exit(1)"
- [x] [BEHAVIOR] 使用 ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS 确保幂等执行
  Test: manual: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const c=fs.readFileSync('packages/brain/migrations/164_fix_missing_columns.sql','utf8');if(!c.includes('ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS started_at'))process.exit(1)"
- [x] [BEHAVIOR] EXPECTED_SCHEMA_VERSION 保持 164 不变
  Test: manual: node -e "const fs=require('fs');const c=fs.readFileSync('packages/brain/src/selfcheck.js','utf8');const m=c.match(/EXPECTED_SCHEMA_VERSION\s*=\s*(\d+)/);if(!m||m[1]!=='164')process.exit(1)"
